{"tid":473232,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇啲思念愛人既古詩","createTime":"2017-11-19T04:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T08:34:22.000Z","uid":152408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1c704d35bdf24a76b598480a358674f31272cd39","tid":473232,"uid":152408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f086c9173b26b0c582a627175fb348621b30f7","tid":473232,"uid":86500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"迢迢牽牛星"},{"pid":"586bc142cd98d85d5b5eece72c5f4bc7752273b3","tid":473232,"uid":76981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"十年生死兩茫茫"},{"pid":"f45f38a15713ed0fb92086866c40f49f485f0f56","tid":473232,"uid":154800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:36:21.000Z","msg":"兩情若是久長時 又豈在朝朝暮暮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcde57573412750c3dc191265479ad6b14cb770","tid":473232,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"相思相見知何日，此時此夜難為情"},{"pid":"c0d53a5d0c0d434811d136f4a9f6addc48482d2b","tid":473232,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相思相見知何日，此時此夜難為情</blockquote><br />\n不過係詞"},{"pid":"767118569e3f36ec9ff3f178f8a451759d7973ab","tid":473232,"uid":153496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"憶君心似西江水，日夜東流無歇時。"},{"pid":"9d79eb7a31d52ea0309de7377006e425f7292fcb","tid":473232,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"長恨歌"},{"pid":"8287e7b9716f7e84b7ae57fe09220569caa1d153","tid":473232,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"我住長江頭 君住長江尾<br />\n日日思君不見君 共飲長江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6091b667da17e054d5ef313c3a920f584e83e3","tid":473232,"uid":155254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"去年今日此門中，人面桃花相映紅；<br />\n人面不知何處去，桃花依舊笑春風。"},{"pid":"b668c5e79d6e133de4c4716881b9b6a5613af047","tid":473232,"uid":44929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:44:03.000Z","msg":"半緣修道半緣君"},{"pid":"fae640fefb7f0c23c017fd80a5de7866a125ecee","tid":473232,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"《無題》<br />\n年代: 唐 作者: 李商隱<br />\n相見時難彆亦難，東風無力百花殘。<br />\n春蠶到死絲方儘，蠟炬成灰淚始乾。<br />\n曉鏡但愁雲鬢改，夜吟應覺月光寒。<br />\n蓬山此去無多路，青鳥殷勤為探看。<br />\n分类标签：愛情詩 思念詩 唐詩三百首 初中<br />\n作品赏析<br />\n<br />\n注釋：<br />\n　　1．無題：唐代以來，有的詩人不願意標出能夠表示主題的題目時，常用&ldquo;<br />\n無題&rdquo;作詩的標題。<br />\n　　2．絲方儘：絲，與&ldquo;思&rdquo;是諧音字，&ldquo;絲方儘&rdquo;意思是除非死了，思念才<br />\n會結束。<br />\n　　3．淚始乾：淚，指燃燒時的蠟燭油，這裡取雙關義，指相思的眼淚。<br />\n　　4．曉鏡：早晨梳妝照鏡子；雲鬢：女子多而美的頭發，這裡比喻青春年華。<br />\n　　5．蓬山：蓬萊山，傳說中海上仙山，比喻被懷念者住的地方。<br />\n　　6．青鳥：神話中為西王母傳遞音訊的信使。<br />\n　　賞析：這是詩人以&ldquo;無題&rdquo;為題目的許多詩歌中最有名的一首寄情詩。整首<br />\n詩的內容圍繞著第一句，尤其是&ldquo;彆亦難&rdquo;三字展開。&ldquo;東風&rdquo;句點了時節，但<br />\n更是對人的相思情狀的比喻。因情的纏綿悱惻，人就像春末凋謝的春花那樣冇了<br />\n生氣。三、四句是相互忠貞不渝、海誓山盟的寫照。五、六句則分彆描述兩人因<br />\n不能相見而惆悵、怨慮，倍感清冷以至衰顏的情狀。唯一可以盼望的是七、八兩<br />\n句中的設想：但願青鳥頻頻傳遞相思情。<br />\n<br />\n（朱麗雲）"},{"pid":"d7f13bd421b210364076f68fbb8d7272c98d47c8","tid":473232,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"Reference:<br />\n<a href=\"http://ft.shicimingju.com/shicimark/sinianshi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fft.shicimingju.com%2Fshicimark%2Fsinianshi.html&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=eb92a89d\" target=\"_blank\">http://ft.shicimingju.com/shicimark/sinianshi.html</a>"},{"pid":"5c834b801af242c35c89e4392d76617e380023a0","tid":473232,"uid":152752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"金風玉露一相逢，便勝卻人間無數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934a37d29d154e1df97a6fc8108e37aa12f277fe","tid":473232,"uid":252982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R3m1Keq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR3m1Keq.jpg&h=66256a81&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}